Script to download subtitles from OpenSubtitles.org

linux/ -> has integration with nautilus-actions to get input from right click context menu. Currently, user has to install nautilus-actions and configure an action for right click to point to the python script, planning to provide an action script configuration file.
osx/ -> Under development, plan to user pyqtx for UI. Possible integration with finder to provide a download subtitle option for video files.
